data.description: Wells Creek, a stunning community, this home was established in 2019. This beautiful home features three bedrooms and two bathrooms. It boasts a spacious layout that is ideal for hosting gatherings. The living area seamlessly flows into a covered and screened lanai, which leads to a beautiful paved patio offering a breathtaking view of the lake that reflects plenty of sunlight to the house.The living areas of this house have tile flooring and the bedrooms have laminate floors. The kitchen has modern cabinets, granite countertops, and stainless steel appliances. Additionally, there is a versatile flex space and a master suite with spacious walk-in closets and a luxurious bathroom equipped with a double sink vanity and a walk-in shower.The Wells Creek neighborhood offers numerous Amenities! Don't miss out on this incredible home! Contact me today for more Information!
